issue.title: Added Wave Component + moon file formating
issue.body:
Main files for working wave component.

Known issues with this implementation:
- When drawing the wave, there seems to be a blue artifact left from the wave. Not sure what is causing this.
- We have to figure out a way to merge canvases. It looks like for every component we write, there needs to be a canvas created, but this just creates a whole new canvas and makes canvas 2x as big.
